### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/health

### List case studies
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/case-studies

### Inspect local dataset
POST http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/inspect/path
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data_path": "examples/synthetic.h5ad"
}

### Run audit from local path
POST http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/audits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data_path": "examples/synthetic.h5ad",
  "output_dir": "results/platform_demo/runs/synthetic_api_demo",
  "batch_key": "batch",
  "label_key": "signal_label",
  "config_path": "configs/singlecell_audit.yaml",
  "background": false
}

### Get jobs
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/jobs

### Optional auth header when OMICSTRUST_API_TOKEN is set
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/jobs
X-OmicsTrust-Token: replace_me
